				<level type="number">1</level>
				<name type="string">Cantrips</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>Sorcerers learn a number of cantrips, or 0-level spells, as noted on the Sorcerer Spells Known Table under &#34;Spells Known.&#34; These spells are cast like any other spell, but they do not consume any slots and may be used again.</p>
